#### CUSTOM
 
# Workflow: I only have 1 active task at all time and previously 
# started task that has been stopped will have their urgency massively
# boosted.
# TODO: create hook to stop all other task when a task is started
# check https://gist.github.com/linuxcaffe/60a773e359d46090d2da78ca7198f709
